      the data it collects from this website. For more information related to Google Analytics, click here: http://www.google.com/intl/en/analytics/privacyoverview.html. For information about and to install Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on, click
      here:</p>
    <p>http://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout?hl=en.</p>

    <p class="subtitle is-3 mt-5">Do we collect any other information?</p>
